    <title>Linux初体验,Debian可爱捏</title>
    <link href="https://homoarea.github.io/2025/02/17/Linux%E5%88%9D%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C-Debian%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E6%8D%8F/"/>
    <id>https://homoarea.github.io/2025/02/17/Linux%E5%88%9D%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C-Debian%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E6%8D%8F/</id>
    <published>2025-02-17T08:58:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-02-17T15:38:21.109Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="什么是Linux？-๑•̀ㅂ•́-و✧"><a href="#什么是Linux？-๑•̀ㅂ•́-و✧" class="headerlink" title="什么是Linux？(๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧"></a>什么是Linux？(๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧</h2><p>常说的Linux(GNU&#x2F;Linux)是免费使用和自由传播的类Unix操作系统(<a class="link"   href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/Linux"  title="查看Linux的详情">详情见wiki<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>)。这里不具体讲解操作系统的构成，先入门Linux使用。</p><p>Linux有众多的发行版，选什么好呢？无疑是 <strong><a class="link"   href="https://www.debian.org/" >Debian<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></strong> 啦！Debian有很大年龄了，派生出了Ubuntu，以其稳定性著称。更别说拥有这么一个好听的名字、好看的logo和自由包容的社区<del>(夹带私货，我有罪)</del>。粉嘟嘟可爱捏～<br>总之我已经等不及了，快点开始罢(客人特有的急性子发作中⚡)。</p><h2 id="安装Debian"><a href="#安装Debian" class="headerlink" title="安装Debian"></a>安装Debian</h2>  <div class="note p-4 mb-4 rounded-small info">    <p>材料：u盘&gt;4GB x1, 个人电脑 x1, 吃饱饭的脑子，没有冻疮的手 </p>  </div><h3 id="制作并使用usb启动盘"><a href="#制作并使用usb启动盘" class="headerlink" title="制作并使用usb启动盘"></a>制作并使用usb启动盘</h3><p>建议下载离线版本，不使用网络下载内容(网速慢)，安装完毕后再使用网络获取软件。<br><a class="link"   href="https://cdimage.debian.org/debian-cd/current/amd64/iso-dvd/debian-12.9.0-amd64-DVD-1.iso" >点击下载 64位Debian<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>或者从<a class="link"   href="https://www.debian.org/distrib/" >官网<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>下载<code>64 位 PC DVD-1 iso</code></p><p>下载软件以制作usb启动盘，对于不同用户：</p><div class="tabs" id="tab-first-unique-name"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#first-unique-name-1">Windows</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#first-unique-name-2">MacOS</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#first-unique-name-3">Linux</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="first-unique-name-1"><p><strong><a class="link"   href="https://rufus.ie/zh/" >下载便携版<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></strong> 或者 <strong><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/balena-io/etcher/releases/" >下载.exe安装文件<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></strong></p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="first-unique-name-2"><p><strong><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/balena-io/etcher/releases/" >下载dmg包<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></strong></p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="first-unique-name-3"><p><strong><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/balena-io/etcher/releases/" >https://github.com/balena-io/etcher/releases/<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></strong><br>你真不会吗，我不信😅</p></div></div></div><p>插上 u盘，使用下好的软件写入 iso映像。<br>.<br>.<br>….<br>…..<br>.<br>….<br>…写入完毕!</p>  <div class="note p-4 mb-4 rounded-small danger">    <p>注意：备份好重要的数据，以免操作不当丢失</p>  </div><ol><li>备份好数据，插入U盘启动盘。</li><li>开机时按F12(F11、F2、DEL、Esc或F8等)快捷键，进入BIOS或启动菜单。</li><li>选择U盘启动项，按回车即可进入U盘启动。</li></ol><h3 id="图形化安装"><a href="#图形化安装" class="headerlink" title="图形化安装"></a>图形化安装</h3><p><a class="link"   href="https://www.cnblogs.com/hopeblaze/articles/18607142" >使用桌面，勾选 □ Debian desktop environment □ KDE Plasma<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></p><h2 id="配置Debian-KDE"><a href="#配置Debian-KDE" class="headerlink" title="配置Debian KDE"></a>配置Debian KDE</h2><h3 id="语言"><a href="#语言" class="headerlink" title="语言"></a>语言</h3><p>点击设置<br>到<code>settings &gt; region and languages &gt; language</code><br><code>修改 &gt; 添加更多 &gt; 简体中文</code>,将简体中文移至最顶部，点击应用，登出后重新登陆。</p><h3 id="体验终端模拟器"><a href="#体验终端模拟器" class="headerlink" title="体验终端模拟器"></a>体验终端模拟器</h3><p>打开终端(Konsole)</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span> --<span class="built_in">help</span></span><br><span class="line">man <span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h3 id="添加用户到-sudoers"><a href="#添加用户到-sudoers" class="headerlink" title="添加用户到 sudoers"></a>添加用户到 sudoers</h3><p>打开终端(Konsole)</p><p><strong>将<code>username</code>替换为你的用户名</strong></p><blockquote><ol><li><code>su -</code></li><li><code>sudo visudo</code></li><li>末尾添加<code>username    ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL</code> ，保存并推出</li><li><code>exit</code></li></ol></blockquote><p>或者</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su -</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;username    ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/sudoers</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>现在可以使用 <code>sudo ls</code></p><h3 id="Debian镜像源-以清华源为例"><a href="#Debian镜像源-以清华源为例" class="headerlink" title="Debian镜像源(以清华源为例)"></a>Debian镜像源(以清华源为例)</h3><p>连接网络<br><a class="link"   href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/debian/" >Debian清华源<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></p><p>Debian 12 (bookworm)</p><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 启用源码源</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 使用非自由软件源</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 强制安全更新使用镜像</li></ul><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;# 默认注释了源码镜像以提高 apt update 速度，如有需要可自行取消注释</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-updates main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-updates main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-backports main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-backports main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"># 以下安全更新软件源包含了官方源与镜像站配置，如有需要可自行修改注释切换</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware&quot;</span> &gt; /etc/apt/sources.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h3 id="常用软件"><a href="#常用软件" class="headerlink" title="常用软件"></a>常用软件</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 更新软件包</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt update &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">sudo</span> upgrade -y</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 分别为信息查看、图形化密钥管理、音视频播放器、直播录像、下载器、输入法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install neofetch seahorse vlc obs-studio qbittorrent fcitx5 fcitx5-chinese-addons</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h3 id="Nvidia驱动-无nvidia显卡跳过"><a href="#Nvidia驱动-无nvidia显卡跳过" class="headerlink" title="Nvidia驱动(无nvidia显卡跳过)"></a>Nvidia驱动(无nvidia显卡跳过)</h3>  <div class="note p-4 mb-4 rounded-small info">    <p>补充：KDE 桌面进不去，不想配置启用 Wayland,可以将 Wayland 改为 X11</p>  </div><p><strong><a class="link"   href="https://www.bilibili.com/opus/880138871710416980" >简洁明了的步骤<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></strong></p><h3 id="外观、主题、KDE插件"><a href="#外观、主题、KDE插件" class="headerlink" title="外观、主题、KDE插件"></a>外观、主题、KDE插件</h3><p>按自己喜欢打开设置调节(其实默认就挺好了)。</p><h3 id="END"><a href="#END" class="headerlink" title="END"></a>END</h3><p>迎接崭新的 Debian 吧。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
